Γ ⊢ a \fB<=>\fR b ↓ 0 :: Int
.SEME

.SEM Γ ⊢ a:E\*<+\*> \fB!=\fR b:E\*<+\*> ↓ True
Γ ⊢ a \fB<=>\fR b ↓ x :: Int,

