.SEM Γ ⊢ a:E\*<+\*> \fB>=\fR b:E\*<+\*> ↓ False
Γ ⊢ a \fB<=>\fR b ↓ -1 :: Int
.SEME

.SEM Γ ⊢ a:E\*<+\*> \fB>=\fR b:E\*<+\*> ↓ True
Γ ⊢ a \fB<=>\fR b ↓ x :: Int,

x ≠ -1
.SEME

.TP
Less than check
