Γ ⊢ expr ↓ v :: Float
.SEME

See IEEE 754 for semantics of ROUND_TOWARD_ZERO (a.k.a., truncation).

.TP
Coerce a value to an string
.SEM Γ ⊢ expr:E\*<+\*> \fBTo\fR \fBStr\fR ↓ PRINTF(\(dq%d\(dq, v) :: Str
Γ ⊢ expr ↓ v :: Int
.SEME
