Check if a number is not-a-number.
.SEM Γ ⊢ expr:E\*<+\*> \fBIs NaN\fR ↓ False
Γ ⊢ expr ↓ v :: Int
.SEME
.SEM Γ ⊢ expr:E\*<+\*> \fBIs NaN\fR ↓ ISNAN(v) :: Bool
Γ ⊢ expr ↓ v :: Float
