.TP
Instantiate a template

.SEM Γ ⊢ source:E\*<+\*> \fB{\fR a:(A / O)+ \fB}\fR ↓ v
Γ ⊢ \fB(Template\fR source \fB{\fR a \fB}) { }\fR ↓ v
.SEME

